      <title>恒大创始人前妻资产被冻结后每月可获 26,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/evergrande-founder-s-ex-wife-allowed-26-000-expenses-after-freeze</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国恒大集团创始人许家印前妻被该开发商清算人提起的诉讼中，英国法院冻结了其资产，并允许其每月支出高达 20,000 英镑（26,187 美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/evergrande-founder-s-ex-wife-allowed-26-000-expenses-after-freeze</guid>
