      <title>对冲基金老板艾伦·霍华德考虑离开伦敦前往日内瓦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/hedge-fund-boss-alan-howard-considers-leaving-london-for-geneva</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Brevan Howard Asset Management 联合创始人艾伦·霍华德 (Alan Howard) 正考虑从伦敦迁往日内瓦。]]></description>
